trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch to a designer view (such as `Design` view in [!INCLUDE[vs_current_short](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]), the markup that describes the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control is parsed.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter til en designer visning (eksempel `Design` Vis i [!INCLUDE[vs_current_short](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]), markup som beskriver den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontrollen analyseres.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>

trans-unit.source: A design-time version of the control is then created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: En utformingen versjon av kontrollen opprettes på utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: When you switch to source view, the design-time control is persisted as markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du bytter til kildevisningen, skal utformingen-kontrollen opprettholdes som markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: The properties of the DataPagerDesigner class provide the following functionality: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.ActionLists%2A> property returns the list of items that are used to create a smart tag panel.
trans-unit.target: Egenskaper for klassen DataPagerDesigner inneholder følgende funksjonalitet: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.ActionLists%2A>egenskapen returnerer liste med elementer som brukes til å opprette et smartkort koden panel.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.ActionLists%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.PagedControlID%2A> property is used as the designer (shadowed) version of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.PagedControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.PagedControlID%2A>Egenskapen brukes som designer (skyggelagt) versjonen av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.PagedControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.PagedControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.PagedControlID%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> property returns a collection of template groups for the templated pager fields of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>Egenskapen returnerer en samling av malen grupper for organisasjonsapper personsøker feltene for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property always returns `true`, which indicates that the designer creates a temporary copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control in order to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>Egenskapen returnerer alltid `true`, noe som angir at det opprettes en midlertidig kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll for å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The methods of the DataPagerDesigner class provide the following functionality: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml%2A> methods return the HTML markup that is used to render the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> at design time.
trans-unit.target: Metoder for klassen DataPagerDesigner inneholder følgende funksjonalitet: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml%2A>metoder returnere HTML-koden som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.Initialize%2A> method prepares the designer to view, edit, and design the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.Initialize%2A>Metoden Klargjør utformeren for å vise, redigere og utforme den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> method is used to add or remove properties from the properties grid for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A>Metoden brukes til å legge til eller Fjern egenskaper fra rutenettet egenskapene for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] creates a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control or a copy of that control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner>klasse når det oppretter den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll eller en kopi av kontrollen på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Gets the list of items that are used to create the smart tag panel for the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter listen over elementer som brukes til å opprette smartkort koden panelet for den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The list of items that are used to create the smart tag panel for the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Listen over elementer som brukes til å opprette smart koden panelet for den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Generates the HTML markup that is used to render the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Genererer HTML-koden som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection is not empty, the GetDesignTimeHtml method refreshes the <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor> object to force the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> method to be called and then calls its base implementation.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samlingen er tom, metoden GetDesignTimeHtml oppdaterer den <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>objekt for å fremtvinge det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A>metoden kalles og kaller deretter base implementeringen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection is empty, the GetDesignTimeHtml method invokes the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml%2A> method to generate the markup.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samlingen er tom, metoden GetDesignTimeHtml aktiverer den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml%2A>metode for å generere koden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataPagerDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The HTML markup that is used to render the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: HTML-koden som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Generates the HTML markup that represents a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control at design time that has no visual representation at run time.
trans-unit.target: Genererer HTML-koden som representerer en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontroll på utformingstidspunktet som har ingen visuell representasjon på kjøretidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: The GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml method is used by the designer to render the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control at design time if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection is empty.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml brukes av designer til å gjengi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontrollere på utformingstidspunktet hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samlingen er tom.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>

trans-unit.source: The GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%28System.String%29> method to create a placeholder that displays the type and the ID of the control, and additional instructions for the user.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%28System.String%29>metode for å opprette en plassholder som viser typen og IDen for kontrollen, og ytterligere instruksjoner for brukeren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%28System.String%29>

trans-unit.source: The HTML markup that represents an empty <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: HTML-koden som representerer et tomt <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the control designer and loads the specified control.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer kontrollen designer og laster inn den angitte kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The designer host calls the Initialize method when it is ready to use the designer to render the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control.
trans-unit.target: Spørringsutformer verten kaller i initialiseringsmetoden når den er klar til å bruke designer til å gjengi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>

trans-unit.source: The Initialize method and its base methods configure properties and connect to events that are required for the designer.
trans-unit.target: I initialiseringsmetoden base metodene konfigurere egenskaper og koble til hendelser som er nødvendig for designer.

trans-unit.source: The `component` parameter is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control that is associated with this designer, or a copy of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control.
trans-unit.target: Den `component` parameteren er av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontrollen som er tilknyttet utformeren eller en kopi av det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>

trans-unit.source: The control being designed.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen blir utformet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value for the designer version of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.PagedControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi for designer-versjonen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.PagedControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.PagedControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.PagedControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: Adds or removes properties from the property grid for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Legger til eller fjerner egenskaper fra egenskapen rutenettet for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The PreFilterProperties method adds a new property to the property grid of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control that corresponds to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.PagedControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden PreFilterProperties legger til en ny egenskap i rutenettet egenskapen for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontrollen som samsvarer med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.PagedControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.PagedControlID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.InTemplateMode%2A> property is set to `true`, the PreFilterProperties method also sets the <xref:System.ComponentModel.BrowsableAttribute> attribute of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to `BrowsableAttribute.No`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.InTemplateMode%2A>er satt til `true`, metoden PreFilterProperties angir også de <xref:System.ComponentModel.BrowsableAttribute>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen `BrowsableAttribute.No`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ComponentModel.BrowsableAttribute> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.InTemplateMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: This prevents pager fields from being deleted by using the `Fields` dialog box when a templated pager field is in template mode.
trans-unit.target: Dette hindrer personsøker felt slettes ved hjelp av den `Fields` dialogboksen når en organisasjonsapper personsøker er i modus for mal.

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the properties that are exposed in the property grid for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: En samling som inneholder egenskapene som vises i rutenettet egenskapen for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of template groups for the templated pager fields of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av malen grupper for organisasjonsapper personsøker feltene for den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property creates a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> objects that represent the template elements in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TemplateGroups oppretter en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>objekter som representerer mal-elementer i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll på utformingstidspunktet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>

trans-unit.source: It adds one element to the collection for each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField> object in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A> collection of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control.
trans-unit.target: Legger den til ett element i samlingen for hver <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField>objekt i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A>samling av den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.Fields%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField>

trans-unit.source: A collection of template groups for the templated pager fields of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: En samling av malen grupper for organisasjonsapper personsøker feltene for den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the designer should use a temporary copy instead of the actual <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control that is associated with the designer in order to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer må bruke en midlertidig kopi i stedet for den faktiske <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> kontrollen som er forbundet med designer for å generere utformingen markup.
